{"id":58,"parent_id":0,"book_id":22563,"content_id":1,"language_id":1,"display_order":58,"title":"“Behold, I Come Quickly; and My Reward Is with Me”","subtitle":"","short_title":56,"uri":"/manual/the-life-and-teachings-of-jesus-and-his-apostles-instructors-guide-rel-211-12/behold-i-come-quickly-and-my-reward-is-with-me","content":[["div",{"id":"head1","uri":"/manual/the-life-and-teachings-of-jesus-and-his-apostles-instructors-guide-rel-211-12/behold-i-come-quickly-and-my-reward-is-with-me.head1"},[".titleNumber","56"],["h1","“Behold, I Come Quickly; and My Reward Is with Me”"]],[".bodyBlock",[".topic",["h2","Theme"],["div",{"id":"p4","uri":"/manual/the-life-and-teachings-of-jesus-and-his-apostles-instructors-guide-rel-211-12/behold-i-come-quickly-and-my-reward-is-with-me.p4"},"The message of John’s vision is one of hope and glory for all who are faithful to the Savior."]],[".topic",["h2","Theme Analysis"],["div",{"id":"f1","uri":"/manual/the-life-and-teachings-of-jesus-and-his-apostles-instructors-guide-rel-211-12/behold-i-come-quickly-and-my-reward-is-with-me.f1"},["ul.content-list alphaCaps",["li",["span.label","A."],["div",[".para","The revelation of John concludes in a crescendo of hope for the glorification of the earth and its inhabitants."]]],["li",["span.label","B."],["div",[".para","As a true prophet of God, John, in an ultimate sense, was a messenger of hope and not of doom!"]]],["li",["span.label","C."],["div",[".para","One can have a lively hope of eternal life only as he obeys the gospel."]]]]]],[".topic",["h2","Study Sources"],[".topic",["h3","New Testament Reading Assignment"],["div",{"id":"p11","uri":"/manual/the-life-and-teachings-of-jesus-and-his-apostles-instructors-guide-rel-211-12/behold-i-come-quickly-and-my-reward-is-with-me.p11"},["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/rev/19"},"Revelation chapters 19 through 22"],"."]],[".topic",["h3","Course Manual"],["div",{"id":"p13","uri":"/manual/the-life-and-teachings-of-jesus-and-his-apostles-instructors-guide-rel-211-12/behold-i-come-quickly-and-my-reward-is-with-me.p13"},"Chapter 56, “Behold, I Come Quickly; and My Reward Is with Me”"]],[".topic",["h3","Standard Works"],["div",{"id":"p15","uri":"/manual/the-life-and-teachings-of-jesus-and-his-apostles-instructors-guide-rel-211-12/behold-i-come-quickly-and-my-reward-is-with-me.p15"},["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/ether/12.4"},"Ether 12:4"],". What has been the great hope of the saints?"],["div",{"id":"p16","uri":"/manual/the-life-and-teachings-of-jesus-and-his-apostles-instructors-guide-rel-211-12/behold-i-come-quickly-and-my-reward-is-with-me.p16"},["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/rev/21.4"},"Revelation 21:4"],". How is it that for the faithful, all tears will be wiped away?"],["div",{"id":"p17","uri":"/manual/the-life-and-teachings-of-jesus-and-his-apostles-instructors-guide-rel-211-12/behold-i-come-quickly-and-my-reward-is-with-me.p17"},["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/76.39-43"},"D&C 76:39-43"],". What is the great hope of the gospel?"],["div",{"id":"p18","uri":"/manual/the-life-and-teachings-of-jesus-and-his-apostles-instructors-guide-rel-211-12/behold-i-come-quickly-and-my-reward-is-with-me.p18"},"Moroni 7:41. What is it that we should hope for?"],["div",{"id":"p19","uri":"/manual/the-life-and-teachings-of-jesus-and-his-apostles-instructors-guide-rel-211-12/behold-i-come-quickly-and-my-reward-is-with-me.p19"},["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/101.23,24"},"D&C 101:23, 24"],". What will the earth be like when every corruptible thing upon it shall be consumed?"],["div",{"id":"p20","uri":"/manual/the-life-and-teachings-of-jesus-and-his-apostles-instructors-guide-rel-211-12/behold-i-come-quickly-and-my-reward-is-with-me.p20"},["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/88.110-16"},"D&C 88:110-16"],". What is the relationship between the era of peace and joy known as the Millennium and the fact that Satan will be bound for one thousand years?"],["div",{"id":"p21","uri":"/manual/the-life-and-teachings-of-jesus-and-his-apostles-instructors-guide-rel-211-12/behold-i-come-quickly-and-my-reward-is-with-me.p21"},["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/1-ne/22.15,16"},"1 Nephi 22:15, 26"],". What is the source of Satan’s power? What will be a great factor in binding him?"],["div",{"id":"p22","uri":"/manual/the-life-and-teachings-of-jesus-and-his-apostles-instructors-guide-rel-211-12/behold-i-come-quickly-and-my-reward-is-with-me.p22"},["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/128.6-9"},"D&C 128:6-9"],". What “books” are to be used in the judgment, according to Joseph Smith?"],["div",{"id":"p23","uri":"/manual/the-life-and-teachings-of-jesus-and-his-apostles-instructors-guide-rel-211-12/behold-i-come-quickly-and-my-reward-is-with-me.p23"},["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/ether/13.8-11"},"Ether 13:8-11"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/45.66-71"},"D&C 45:66-71"],". How many Jerusalems will exist during the Millennium?"],["div",{"id":"p24","uri":"/manual/the-life-and-teachings-of-jesus-and-his-apostles-instructors-guide-rel-211-12/behold-i-come-quickly-and-my-reward-is-with-me.p24"},["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/130.9"},"D&C 130:9"],". What will be the great inheritance of the meek of the earth? (See",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/matt/5.5"},"Matthew 5:5"],".)"]],[".topic",["h3","Basic Library"],["div",{"id":"p26","uri":"/manual/the-life-and-teachings-of-jesus-and-his-apostles-instructors-guide-rel-211-12/behold-i-come-quickly-and-my-reward-is-with-me.p26"},["span.emphasis","Teachings,"],"pp. 65-66. The great promise of the gospel that was extended to the faithful."],["div",{"id":"p27","uri":"/manual/the-life-and-teachings-of-jesus-and-his-apostles-instructors-guide-rel-211-12/behold-i-come-quickly-and-my-reward-is-with-me.p27"},["span.emphasis","Teachings,"],"p. 359. The Saints have the greatest hope."],["div",{"id":"p28","uri":"/manual/the-life-and-teachings-of-jesus-and-his-apostles-instructors-guide-rel-211-12/behold-i-come-quickly-and-my-reward-is-with-me.p28"},["span.emphasis","Discourses,"],"pp. 115-16. The great work of the Millennium."],["div",{"id":"p29","uri":"/manual/the-life-and-teachings-of-jesus-and-his-apostles-instructors-guide-rel-211-12/behold-i-come-quickly-and-my-reward-is-with-me.p29"},["span.emphasis","DS,"],"3:55-79. The Millennium and the New Jerusalem."],["div",{"id":"p30","uri":"/manual/the-life-and-teachings-of-jesus-and-his-apostles-instructors-guide-rel-211-12/behold-i-come-quickly-and-my-reward-is-with-me.p30"},["span.emphasis","A of F,"],"pp. 368-71. Conditions during the Millennium."],["div",{"id":"p31","uri":"/manual/the-life-and-teachings-of-jesus-and-his-apostles-instructors-guide-rel-211-12/behold-i-come-quickly-and-my-reward-is-with-me.p31"},["span.emphasis","M of F,"],"pp. 341-43. Hope motivates repentance."],["div",{"id":"p32","uri":"/manual/the-life-and-teachings-of-jesus-and-his-apostles-instructors-guide-rel-211-12/behold-i-come-quickly-and-my-reward-is-with-me.p32"},"Ezra Taft Benson in",["span.emphasis","CR,"],"Oct. 1974, pp. 90-94. Overcoming despair and gaining the hope of eternal life!"]],[".topic",["h3","Additional Sources"],["div",{"id":"p34","uri":"/manual/the-life-and-teachings-of-jesus-and-his-apostles-instructors-guide-rel-211-12/behold-i-come-quickly-and-my-reward-is-with-me.p34"},"Bruce R. McConkie,",["span.emphasis","Mormon Doctrine,"],"pp. 366-68. The hope of Israel."],["div",{"id":"p35","uri":"/manual/the-life-and-teachings-of-jesus-and-his-apostles-instructors-guide-rel-211-12/behold-i-come-quickly-and-my-reward-is-with-me.p35"},"Marion G. Romney in",["span.emphasis","CR,"],"Apr. 1951, pp. 20-24. Righteousness brings hope."],["div",{"id":"p36","uri":"/manual/the-life-and-teachings-of-jesus-and-his-apostles-instructors-guide-rel-211-12/behold-i-come-quickly-and-my-reward-is-with-me.p36"},"Marion G. Romney in",["span.emphasis","CR,"],"Oct. 1966, pp. 50-54. What hope for the future do the righteous have?"],["div",{"id":"p37","uri":"/manual/the-life-and-teachings-of-jesus-and-his-apostles-instructors-guide-rel-211-12/behold-i-come-quickly-and-my-reward-is-with-me.p37"},"Joseph Fielding Smith,",["span.emphasis","The Way to Perfection,"],"pp. 298-304, 308-13. The Millennium."],["div",{"id":"p38","uri":"/manual/the-life-and-teachings-of-jesus-and-his-apostles-instructors-guide-rel-211-12/behold-i-come-quickly-and-my-reward-is-with-me.p38"},"Bruce R. McConkie in",["span.emphasis","DNTC"],"3:562-95. The culmination of the earth’s history."],["div",{"id":"f2","uri":"/manual/the-life-and-teachings-of-jesus-and-his-apostles-instructors-guide-rel-211-12/behold-i-come-quickly-and-my-reward-is-with-me.f2"},["table",["tbody",["tr",["td",{"colspan":"1","rowspan":"1"},[".para","T"]],["td",{"colspan":"1","rowspan":"1"},["div",{"id":"f3","uri":"/manual/the-life-and-teachings-of-jesus-and-his-apostles-instructors-guide-rel-211-12/behold-i-come-quickly-and-my-reward-is-with-me.f3"},["ol.number",["li",["span.label","8."],[".para","During the Millennium there will be a great missionary effort among those not yet converted to the gospel. (",["span.emphasis","DS,"],"3:64-65.)"]]]]]],["tr",["td",{"colspan":"1","rowspan":"1"},[".para","T"]],["td",{"colspan":"1","rowspan":"1"},["div",{"id":"f4","uri":"/manual/the-life-and-teachings-of-jesus-and-his-apostles-instructors-guide-rel-211-12/behold-i-come-quickly-and-my-reward-is-with-me.f4"},["ol.number",["li",["span.label","9."],[".para","The earth will be transfigured at the outset of the Millennium. (",["span.emphasis","DS,"],"3:56-57.)"]]]]]],["tr",["td",{"colspan":"1","rowspan":"1"},[".para","F"]],["td",{"colspan":"1","rowspan":"1"},["div",{"id":"f5","uri":"/manual/the-life-and-teachings-of-jesus-and-his-apostles-instructors-guide-rel-211-12/behold-i-come-quickly-and-my-reward-is-with-me.f5"},["ol.number",["li",["span.label","10."],[".para","Resurrected beings will assist with temple work during the Millennium. (",["span.emphasis","DS,"],"2:178.)"]]]]]],["tr",["td",{"colspan":"1","rowspan":"1"},[".para","F"]],["td",{"colspan":"1","rowspan":"1"},["div",{"id":"f6","uri":"/manual/the-life-and-teachings-of-jesus-and-his-apostles-instructors-guide-rel-211-12/behold-i-come-quickly-and-my-reward-is-with-me.f6"},["ol.number",["li",["span.label","11."],[".para","Apparently, there will be no carnivorous animals during the Millennium. (",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/isa/65.25"},"Isaiah 65:25"],".)"]]]]]],["tr",["td",{"colspan":"1","rowspan":"1"},[".para","F"]],["td",{"colspan":"1","rowspan":"1"},["div",{"id":"f7","uri":"/manual/the-life-and-teachings-of-jesus-and-his-apostles-instructors-guide-rel-211-12/behold-i-come-quickly-and-my-reward-is-with-me.f7"},["ol.number",["li",["span.label","12."],[".para","Inaccuracies in genealogical records of past generations will be corrected during the Millennium. (",["span.emphasis","DS,"],"2:177-78.)"]]]]]]]]]],[".topic",["h3","An Overview of the Final Chapters of Revelation (A Review)"],["div",{"id":"p50","uri":"/manual/the-life-and-teachings-of-jesus-and-his-apostles-instructors-guide-rel-211-12/behold-i-come-quickly-and-my-reward-is-with-me.p50"},"It could be beneficial to review the chart on the book of Revelation included in the map section of the course manual. The last seven boxes emphasize the content of",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/rev/19"},"Revelation chapters 19-22"],"."]]],[".topic",["h2","Some Suggestions for Presentation"],[".subtitle","(Ideas Other Teachers Have Used)"],[".topic",["h3","The Gospel of Hope Versus the Way of Despair (A Discussion)"],["div",{"id":"f8","uri":"/manual/the-life-and-teachings-of-jesus-and-his-apostles-instructors-guide-rel-211-12/behold-i-come-quickly-and-my-reward-is-with-me.f8"},"The instructor could feature the hopefulness of the gospel as contrasted with the despair of the world, using the following scriptural examples:",["ol.number",["li",["span.label","1."],[".para","One who had hope.",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/ether/15.34"},"Ether 15:34"],"."],[".para","One who despaired.",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/alma/30.52-60"},"Alma 30:52-60"],"."]],["li",["span.label","2."],[".para","The hope of a saint.",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/philip/4.13"},"Philippians 4:13"],"."],[".para","The way of the world.",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/alma/30.17"},"Alma 30:17"],"."]],["li",["span.label","3."],[".para","The hope of eternal life.",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/ether/12.4"},"Ether 12:4"],"."],[".para","The death and despair of the world.",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/alma/30.18"},"Alma 30:18"],"."]],["li",["span.label","4."],[".para","Earthly trials in the gospel context.",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/mosiah/24.14,15"},"Mosiah 24:14, 15"],"."],[".para","The struggle of those who are without God.",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/morm/5.2"},"Mormon 5:2"],"."]],["li",["span.label","5."],[".para","The more exalted hope of the faithful.",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/ether/12.32"},"Ether 12:32"],"."],[".para","The despair of sin.",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/moro/10.22"},"Moroni 10:22"],"."]],["li",["span.label","6."],[".para","The atonement and resurrection of Christ provide the greatest hope.",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/1-cor/15.19,20"},"1 Corinthians 15:19, 20"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/1-jn/3.2"},"1 John 3:2"],"."]],["li",["span.label","7."],[".para","All is vanity without the hope of the gospel.",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/eccl/1.2-11"},"Ecclesiastes 1:2-11"],"."]]]]],[".topic",["h3","True or False Test (A Discussion)"],["div",{"id":"p68","uri":"/manual/the-life-and-teachings-of-jesus-and-his-apostles-instructors-guide-rel-211-12/behold-i-come-quickly-and-my-reward-is-with-me.p68"},"The following quiz could promote a discussion on conditions during the Millennium:"],["div",{"id":"f9","uri":"/manual/the-life-and-teachings-of-jesus-and-his-apostles-instructors-guide-rel-211-12/behold-i-come-quickly-and-my-reward-is-with-me.f9"},["table",["tbody",["tr",["td",{"colspan":"1","rowspan":"1"},[".para","F"]],["td",{"colspan":"1","rowspan":"1"},["div",{"id":"f10","uri":"/manual/the-life-and-teachings-of-jesus-and-his-apostles-instructors-guide-rel-211-12/behold-i-come-quickly-and-my-reward-is-with-me.f10"},["ol.number",["li",["span.label","1."],[".para","Children born during the Millennium will grow up with immortal bodies. (",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/101.30,31"},"D&C 101:30, 31"],".)"]]]]]],["tr",["td",{"colspan":"1","rowspan":"1"},[".para","T"]],["td",{"colspan":"1","rowspan":"1"},["div",{"id":"f11","uri":"/manual/the-life-and-teachings-of-jesus-and-his-apostles-instructors-guide-rel-211-12/behold-i-come-quickly-and-my-reward-is-with-me.f11"},["ol.number",["li",["span.label","2."],[".para","During the Millennium, the earth will return to a condition like that in which it existed prior to the flood. (",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/133.23,24"},"D&C 133:23, 24"],".)"]]]]]],["tr",["td",{"colspan":"1","rowspan":"1"},[".para","T"]],["td",{"colspan":"1","rowspan":"1"},["div",{"id":"f12","uri":"/manual/the-life-and-teachings-of-jesus-and-his-apostles-instructors-guide-rel-211-12/behold-i-come-quickly-and-my-reward-is-with-me.f12"},["ol.number",["li",["span.label","3."],[".para","There may well be non-Mormons on the earth during the Millennium. (",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/zech/14.16,17"},"Zechariah 14:16, 17"],";",["span.emphasis","DS,"],"3:63-64.)"]]]]]],["tr",["td",{"colspan":"1","rowspan":"1"},[".para","T"]],["td",{"colspan":"1","rowspan":"1"},["div",{"id":"f13","uri":"/manual/the-life-and-teachings-of-jesus-and-his-apostles-instructors-guide-rel-211-12/behold-i-come-quickly-and-my-reward-is-with-me.f13"},["ol.number",["li",["span.label","4."],[".para","The sealed portion of the Book of Mormon may come forth during the Millennium. (",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/27.7,8,10"},"2 Nephi 27:7, 8, 10"],".)"]]]]]],["tr",["td",{"colspan":"1","rowspan":"1"},[".para","T"]],["td",{"colspan":"1","rowspan":"1"},["div",{"id":"f14","uri":"/manual/the-life-and-teachings-of-jesus-and-his-apostles-instructors-guide-rel-211-12/behold-i-come-quickly-and-my-reward-is-with-me.f14"},["ol.number",["li",["span.label","5."],[".para","In its millennial state, the earth will be much as it was before the Fall. (",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/isa/65.17-25"},"Isaiah 65:17-25"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/101.26-34"},"D&C 101:26-34"],".)"]]]]]],["tr",["td",{"colspan":"1","rowspan":"1"},[".para","T"]],["td",{"colspan":"1","rowspan":"1"},["div",{"id":"f15","uri":"/manual/the-life-and-teachings-of-jesus-and-his-apostles-instructors-guide-rel-211-12/behold-i-come-quickly-and-my-reward-is-with-me.f15"},["ol.number",["li",["span.label","6."],[".para","The sentence “They shall beat their swords into plowshares” has reference to world peace, which will exist during the Millennium. (See previous references.)"]]]]]],["tr",["td",{"colspan":"1","rowspan":"1"},[".para","T"]],["td",{"colspan":"1","rowspan":"1"},["div",{"id":"f16","uri":"/manual/the-life-and-teachings-of-jesus-and-his-apostles-instructors-guide-rel-211-12/behold-i-come-quickly-and-my-reward-is-with-me.f16"},["ol.number",["li",["span.label","7."],[".para","Satan will literally be restrained from his work of opposition during the Millennium, primarily through the righteousness of the people. (",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/rev/20.2,3"},"Revelation 20:2, 3"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/1-ne/22.26"},"1 Nephi 22:26"],".)"]]]]]]]]]]]]],"refs":null}
